---
// src/pages/terms.astro
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout 
  title="Terms & Conditions: Disclaimer of Veterinary Liability | petfoodcal" 
  description="Review the terms and conditions for using petfoodcal. Understand that our calculations are guides, not professional veterinary advice."
  canonicalUrl="https://petfoodcal.vercel.app/terms"
>
  <!-- Hero Banner -->
  <section class="bg-canvas-soft border-b border-hairline" style="padding: 80px 24px 64px;">
    <div class="max-w-[700px] mx-auto text-center">
      <span class="font-mono text-[12px] uppercase tracking-wider text-body inline-block" style="margin-bottom: 12px;">User Agreement</span>
      <h1 class="display-lg font-semibold tracking-tight text-ink" style="margin-bottom: 16px;">Terms and Conditions</h1>
      <p class="text-body leading-relaxed" style="font-size: 15px;">
        Please read these terms carefully before using our pet food calculator.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Content -->
  <section class="bg-canvas" style="padding: 64px 24px 80px;">
    <div class="max-w-[700px] mx-auto leading-relaxed text-body" style="font-size: 15px; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 40px;">
      
      <!-- Veterinary Disclaimer -->
      <div class="bg-error-soft/30 border border-error/20 rounded-md text-error-deep" style="padding: 20px; font-size: 14px;">
        <strong class="block font-semibold" style="margin-bottom: 6px;">⚠️ IMPORTANT VETERINARY DISCLAIMER</strong>
        The calculations, portion estimates, and feeding splits generated by petfoodcal are intended strictly for educational and informational purposes. They are based on general metabolic guidelines for average dogs and cats. They do not constitute professional veterinary advice, diagnosis, or treatment. Every pet is unique, and dietary needs can vary significantly based on underlying health issues, genetics, and environment.
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="display-sm font-semibold text-ink" style="margin-bottom: 12px;">1. Assume Risk for Calculations (Use at Your Own Risk)</h2>
        <p style="margin-bottom: 16px;">
          By accessing or using petfoodcal, you acknowledge that you do so at your own risk. We make no guarantees regarding the accuracy, completeness, or suitability of the nutritional calculations for your specific pet. 
        </p>
        <p>
          Always monitor your pet's physical condition, body weight, rib coverage, and stool quality. We strongly recommend consulting with a licensed veterinarian or a certified veterinary nutritionist before implementing any major changes to your pet's diet, especially raw feeding or home-cooked formulas.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div style="padding-top: 24px; border-top: 1px solid var(--color-hairline);">
        <h2 class="display-sm font-semibold text-ink" style="margin-bottom: 12px;">2. Recognize Limitations of Liability</h2>
        <p>
          Under no circumstances shall petfoodcal, its owners, or contributors be held liable for any direct, indirect, incidental, consequential, or punitive damages resulting from the use of this calculator, including but not limited to pet illness, injury, nutritional deficiencies, obesity, or veterinary expenses.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div style="padding-top: 24px; border-top: 1px solid var(--color-hairline);">
        <h2 class="display-sm font-semibold text-ink" style="margin-bottom: 12px;">3. Follow Acceptable Use Rules</h2>
        <p style="margin-bottom: 16px;">
          You are permitted to use this tool for personal, non-commercial purposes. You must not:
        </p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-5 text-body" style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 8px;">
          <li>Attempt to scrape, reverse engineer, or exploit the calculator code.</li>
          <li>Embed this tool inside other websites or applications without explicit permission.</li>
          <li>Represent the generated portion sheets as official veterinary prescriptions.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div style="padding-top: 24px; border-top: 1px solid var(--color-hairline);">
        <h2 class="display-sm font-semibold text-ink" style="margin-bottom: 12px;">4. Respect Intellectual Property Rights</h2>
        <p>
          The layout, designs, custom calculator logic, code configurations, and SEO textual copy on petfoodcal are protected by copyright laws. Unauthorized reproduction or redistribution of this intellectual property is prohibited.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div style="padding-top: 24px; border-top: 1px solid var(--color-hairline);">
        <h2 class="display-sm font-semibold text-ink" style="margin-bottom: 12px;">5. Accept Policy Modifications</h2>
        <p>
          We reserve the right to modify these Terms and Conditions at any time without prior notice. Continued use of this website following any adjustments signifies your agreement to the modified terms.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
